	#bio
		p
			| I'm a senior at Olin College of Engineering studying Electrical Engineering and Computer Science. I am interested in using technology to make educational tools, natural language processing, software development, UX design, and artificial intelligence.
	#social-icons
		a(href='https://github.com/jnazare', id="social")
